collection.name: Champions Ascension
collection.description:
Meet the glorious 7622 champions who have ascended to the status of Prime Eternal. These Divine few have no equal in the arena, and receive the highest level of in game benefits. Prime Eternals will never be minted again, and give you access to the growing fantasy world Massina. Claim your Prime Eternal Champion, to play in Champions: Ascension a AAA play-to-earn game by Jam City.

[Website](http://champions.io/) | [Discord](https://discord.gg/championsascension) | [Twitter](https://www.twitter.com/ChampionsIO) | [Medium](https://medium.com/@ChampionsP2E)
 
Sister Collections: [Pets of Massina](https://opensea.io/collection/championsascensionpet) | [Imperial Gallery](https://opensea.io/collection/champions-ascension-imperial-gallery)
